{"tid":951202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發!] [齊昕再現〡原諒龍蝦媽暴打]婚事被迫告吹癲喪4年 母女拖實精神行街：我幾孝順","createTime":"2018-12-22T06:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T08:51:57.000Z","uid":90287,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fba35c37d05f4aba4217c5a0c98cd6840f80335","tid":951202,"uid":90287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181222/644762?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181222%2F644762%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ZH4yc4t%2FNb3Zc6B%2FQrMq50bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=11ad1607\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181222%2F644762%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=65225ab2\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181222/644762?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n齊昕拖實媽咪逛街，大家有傾有講，明顯關係復和，感情好好。媽咪着衫時，她更幫手，輕拍褸上的塵，這個女兒非常貼心。難怪齊昕自言，心底裡其實幾孝順。<br />\n<br />\n不過可以行到今日，絕不容易。過去齊昕曾在Facebook留言，踢爆話：「媽媽推我埋牆、摑我，仲鬧『死蠢X、周街被人X、同人上床呀嘛、去做雞呀』，用腳踢我，搞到我跌低，撞埋書枱個枱角。仲威脅話要報警，地氈式搜查我間房。」<br />\n<br />\n關係最差時，她甚至好決絕地表示，不想在媽媽的喪禮出現。幸好兩母女沒隔夜仇，始終這幾年是龍蝦媽陪她走過的。<br />\n<br />\n14年齊昕停學返港，想不到開始了苦難的四年幾。當時英國倫敦政治經濟學院師兄男朋友Michael，畢業返港，齊昕跟他返港，更計劃結婚。但有傳梁振英認為出身中產家庭的Michael，父母在政商界沒人脈，不適合齊昕。他們因為壓力而分手，齊昕話欠Michael好多。<br />\n<br />\nMichael好努力做投資工作，同時重新上市，約會其他異性。而齊昕就陷入低谷，一直對抗情緒病，這幾年的經歷，令她覺得大部人都是人渣。<br />\n<br />\n這幾年跌跌撞撞，可能現在是她過得最平靜的日子。"},{"pid":"65258b68d5d67b366adc206c52df0b676f5bf602","tid":951202,"uid":119605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"睇相好似肥左好多咁"},{"pid":"c9994fbd4d9f11013121d4b6ef14ef7f8f407a3e","tid":951202,"uid":57047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"Michael而家娶左第個<br />\n仔都生埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2ba1df78165dda810cee35d154c7aa44b7065a","tid":951202,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65258b68d5d67b366adc206c52df0b676f5bf602","tid":951202,"uid":119605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"睇相好似肥左好多咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"應該50kg變80都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8684a5c893290d53437bc1d81713181ae131d6","tid":951202,"uid":35752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁肥"},{"pid":"15ff5f884a62626b5b1cfc2ecc1010b20191272d","tid":951202,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"如果689做外父會有咩事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日日like佢fb po t<br />\n日日幫佢聯辦律師出信"}]}